
	<div class="left info">
		<h1>What is this?</h1>
		<p>
			Dots&amp;Boxes is becoming a super-charged multiplayer game based on the traditional
			Dot Game first published in 1889 by Édouard Lucas. It's currently under development and 
			soon you'll be ready to play it and rock on.
		</p>
		<br/><br/>

	<br/><br/>
